README
======

General
-------

Dust Racing is a tile-based 2D racing game written in Qt/OpenGL.
Dust Racing is licensed under GNU GPLv3.

Source code
-----------

The source tree includes source code for the track editor and
the game itself. The game uses an 2D engine called MiniCore
written by Jussi Lind. The code is documented by using
Doxygen tags.

Source tree layout:

src/game/
src/game/MiniCore/
src/editor/

See INSTALL for build / install instruction.


-- Jussi Lind <jussi.lind@iki.fi>
